org.apache.drill.metastore.rdbms.components.tables

Class RdbmsTables

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.drill.metastore.rdbms.components.tables.RdbmsTables
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Tables, Operations<TableMetadataUnit>, RdbmsMetastoreContext<TableMetadataUnit>

    public class RdbmsTables
extends Object
implements Tables, RdbmsMetastoreContext<TableMetadataUnit>
    Metastore Tables component which stores tables metadata in the corresponding RDBMS tables: TABLES, SEGMENTS, FILES, ROW_GROUPS, PARTITIONS. Provides methods to read and modify tables metadata.
